elements.name: Goes to wonder world college page

steps.name: The user goes to the "loginUrl" address

elements.name: When the user enters the correct password combination in the new password, "password has been changed successfully." should receive your message

steps.name: The user clicks Student Login button on wonder world college page
The user enters valid username in Username textbox on User Login page
The user enters valid password in Password textbox on User Login page
The user clicks Sing In buton
The user clicks profile image on the opened page
The user clicks the Change Password button in the drop-down menu
The user types the current password into the Current Password textbox on the Change Password page

The user types a new password in the New Password textbox on the Change Password page, not less than six characters, with the correct password combination containing uppercase letters and one special character
The user correctly retypes the newly created password into the Confirm Password textbox on the Change Password page
The user clicks save button on Change Password page
